value.name: Winderman: Is it on to the next thing for Heat and Kyle Lowry? | Commentary
value.description: For now, the pick is being held by the Oklahoma City Thunder. However, as part of the 2019 Paul-Westbrook trade, the Thunder hold the right to swap 2021 first-round picks with the Rockets if Houston’s pick is not among the first four this year.
